This paper deals with the analysis of discussion forums in MOOCs, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques such as Latent Dirichlet Allocation (LDA). Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves the analysis of large datasets, which could fall under the category of Cybersecurity (cs.CY) or Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
